{"id":"095ab8de-9578-4ef4-a2a1-88fee05aacb0","name":"Simond","description":"<img draggable=\"true\" style=\"margin: 0px auto;\" src=\"https://files.catbox.moe/02fewt.gif\"><p>⚔️ | Cold, your grace? <em>Where you and your personal knight are on a road trip</em></p><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/951c142c-c7bc-4b16-9ac4-f7950fc28230_83161540-1688-4aca-bfd5-bcb6ad9d0bd9.webp?width=1000\"><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/951c142c-c7bc-4b16-9ac4-f7950fc28230_d2aa4e50-c5c2-45a6-be4a-de5879899923.webp?width=1000\"><p style=\"text-align: center\">Helloooo! I am particpating in <a href=\"https://janitorai.com/profiles/ae3b8516-54d5-4469-8557-6dcf808128d0_profile-of-iorveths\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">Io </a>and <a href=\"https://janitorai.com/profiles/fa479f59-71a0-4296-a24d-6e8ca1c3d6fa_profile-of-veseii\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">Ves</a>' Summer Bot exchange!</p><p style=\"text-align: center\">I was paired with <a href=\"https://janitorai.com/profiles/11778b33-00bf-43b4-ac15-dd5864d95f0f_profile-of-maddieismystar\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">MaddieIsMyStar</a>!</p><p style=\"text-align: center\">I had so much fun, and I impulsively (as in, two days before the event) decided to make a second bot since I struggled to chose from their frankly diverse wishlist!</p><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/951c142c-c7bc-4b16-9ac4-f7950fc28230_5dce2bac-06ea-413e-8069-9aee26f817ab.webp?width=1000\"><h1 style=\"text-align: center\"><a href=\"https://janitorai.com/characters/b4a1141b-903c-430d-a8d9-d546b329284d_character-edwin-crauford\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">FIRST EXCHANGE BOT HERE</a></h1><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/951c142c-c7bc-4b16-9ac4-f7950fc28230_33e279a8-8f82-43aa-a440-e44d0fcc974c.webp?width=1000\"><p>Also, this is FemPOV just like my first bot. I will not be changing it, I will not be making alts. Maddie requested femPOV preference in their wish list. I am sorry, I love you guys but I make 97% anyPOV and any comments asking for it to be changed/and alt will be deleted. This is a common occurrence on all femPOV bots so I am preemptively stating it here.</p><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/951c142c-c7bc-4b16-9ac4-f7950fc28230_6ddb0a60-b592-4245-8662-74ba75bbd565.webp?width=1000\">","personality":"","scenario":"","first_message":"","avatar":"951c142c-c7bc-4b16-9ac4-f7950fc28230_1ec3dae8-c540-476f-9596-ba61c4bfb48c.webp","creator":"gunko","creator_verified":true,"nsfw":true,"tags":["👨 Male","🧑‍🎨 OC","📚 Fictional","🏰 Historical","❤️‍🩹 Fluff","👩 FemPov"],"chats":5677,"messages":113198,"created_at":"2024-07-14T23:59:43.785867+00:00"}